<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About | InkScribe</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css">
    <style>
        /* About Page Specific Styles */
        .about-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 3rem auto;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease;
        }

        .about-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .about-title {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            background: var(--gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .about-subtitle {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .about-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
        }

        .about-text {
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .about-text p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .about-features {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .about-features li {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .about-features li::before {
            content: 'â†’';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .about-image {
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            height: fit-content;
        }

        .about-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .about-team {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        .team-title {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .team-members {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .team-member {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .team-member:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .member-image {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
            border: 3px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .member-name {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .member-role {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .social-link {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .social-link:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .about-image {
                order: -1;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header.ejs') %>

    <div class="about-container">
        <div class="about-header">
            <h1 class="about-title">Our Story</h1>
            <p class="about-subtitle">Discover the passion behind InkScribe and the people who make it all possible</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-text">
                <p>Welcome to InkScribe, where words come to life. Founded in 2023, we set out to create a platform that empowers writers of all levels to share their thoughts, stories, and ideas with the world.</p>
                
                <p>What started as a simple blogging tool has evolved into a vibrant community of thinkers, creators, and storytellers. We believe everyone has a unique voice worth hearing.</p>
                
                <h3>Why Choose InkScribe?</h3>
                <ul class="about-features">
                    <li>Beautiful, distraction-free writing environment</li>
                    <li>Simple yet powerful editing tools</li>
                    <li>Built for writers, by writers</li>
                    <li>Privacy-focused platform</li>
                    <li>Constantly evolving with community feedback</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1455390582262-044cdead277a?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Writing desk with notebook and pen">
            </div>

            <div class="about-team">
                <h3 class="team-title">Meet The Team</h3>
                <div class="team-members">
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/43.jpg" alt="Sarah Johnson" class="member-image">
                        <h4 class="member-name">Sarah Johnson</h4>
                        <p class="member-role">Founder & Lead Developer</p>
                        <div class="social-links">
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/32.jpg" alt="Michael Chen" class="member-image">
                        <h4 class="member-name">Michael Chen</h4>
                        <p class="member-role">UX Designer</p>
                        <div class="social-links">
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-dribbble"></i></a>
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-behance"></i></a>
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/65.jpg" alt="Emma Rodriguez" class="member-image">
                        <h4 class="member-name">Emma Rodriguez</h4>
                        <p class="member-role">Community Manager</p>
                        <div class="social-links">
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fab fa-discord"></i></a>
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>

    <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>